column5: Hey guys and gals so Im sitting here wishin i was fish looking over a bunch of fishing pictures that i have taken over the past little while. so I decided to share with you guys ! and many more to come!  Feel free to post pictures of your own adventures! i need some new fish pics to look at!
looks like a great start to the season to me! Thanks for sharing.
(had to add this pig we caught and released out of simcoe)
one of many from huntsville area Scugog walleye little gator from scugog

(she likes fishin and takes the fish off! haha what more can i ask for?!) one of the many cool under water shots with the new z33 yes she caught this.. and no she doesnt have magic powers.. theres a fork holding it up.. but you cant even tell
lets go then
haha now were talkin Ryan.. heres the catch.. my boat is off the water right now.. im waiting on plywood for the deck wich is about 2 weeks late
once shes good we can hook her up to the jeep and go... or if you know any good shore spots, lol.
nice fish man!  so when are you taking me out, LOL!
Some beauties!!  Looking forward to getting out there again myself....can hear that musky calling my name.
A great start to the season! Nice pics!
ok admit it... 90% of all of you clicked to enlarge this pictures of the girl!.... admit it you did lol  :whistling:

ya just waiting on my buddies for some of the better bass pics..!      haha I dont blame you I love her shes the best.. and even better she puts up with my addiction to fishin! and well some times even joins me! and well I just split on a new set up for her.. Quantum Energy Pti 10 spinning reel on a 6'9 turd R-Type Dropshot rod.. she loves it !
So what's yer point?  JF
obviously!!!
is there a guy in this conversation?  I don't see one...
hahaha
Congrats on a great season so far fish-meister Thanks for sharing Leechman
Dang some nice looking pics there looks like your having a good season
Guess where she is when your out fishing........    Just kidding, nice pics!!!
Giggity Giggidy.... for the fish  Great start to the season, nice mix and good sizes.
Nice job man!
and its sad to say i havnt been fishing nearly as much this year as i did last year !
HUGE start if you ask me!
